            <supports>Bard, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard, Rogue</supports>
            <description>
                <p>Improbability erupts invisibly all around you. All creatures in initiative order within range must re-roll their initiatives at the top of the next round. Creatures on a different plane are unaffected.</p>
